Arvin Industries Inc said itsshareholders at the annual meeting voted to increase authorizedcommon shares to 50 mln from 30 mln.    The company told shareholders that the offering of 1.7 mlncommon shares in January raised 50 mln dlrs, and the 500 sharesof variable rated preferred stock offered in February alsoraised 50 mln dlrs. The company said it also placed 150 mlndlrs in long-term debt in March. Reuter&#3;